<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Atelier Sucré | Pastelería artesanal</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Pastelería artesanal de estética minimalista. Tortas, mini pastelería y box dulces con una identidad limpia, elegante y delicada." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #fcfaf7;
      --bg-soft: #f6f1ea;
      --panel: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
      --text: #2d2824;
      --muted: #7f766d;
      --line: rgba(45, 40, 36, 0.08);
      --accent: #b9aa97;
      --accent-dark: #8e7d69;
      --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(73, 55, 38, 0.08);
      --radius-xl: 34px;
      --radius-lg: 26px;
      --radius-md: 18px;
      --container: 1180px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(242, 233, 223, 0.65), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #fdfbf8 0%, #fcfaf7 45%, #f8f4ef 100%);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
    img { display: block; width: 100%; }
    .container { width: min(var(--container), calc(100% - 34px)); margin: 0 auto; }

    .topbar {
      min-height: 44px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.58);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(252, 250, 247, 0.82);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.05);
    }

    .nav {
      min-height: 82px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.08);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(66, 47, 34, 0.05);
    }

    .brand-copy {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .brand-copy strong {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.45rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .brand-copy span {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 4px;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 28px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.94rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      transition: 0.2s ease;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .btn-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .btn {
      border: 0;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 14px 22px;
      font-size: 0.94rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease, opacity 0.18s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: #2f2a26;
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(47, 42, 38, 0.16);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.76);
      color: var(--text);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.08);
    }

    .menu-btn {
      display: none;
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.74);
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .mobile-panel {
      display: none;
      padding: 0 0 16px;
    }

    .mobile-panel.open { display: block; }

    .mobile-links {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .mobile-links a,
    .mobile-links .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .mobile-links a {
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.76);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.08);
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 62px 0 30px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.02fr 0.98fr;
      gap: 34px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.74);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.07);
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      margin: 18px 0 14px;
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 6vw, 6rem);
      line-height: 0.9;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      max-width: 11ch;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero p {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 620px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.95;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .hero-notes {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .note-pill {
      padding: 11px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.07);
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero-visual {
      position: relative;
    }

    .hero-card {
      min-height: 680px;
      border-radius: 40px;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), rgba(45,40,36,0.18)),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519864600265-abb23847ef2c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80') center/cover;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .hero-card::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(32,25,20,0.08), rgba(32,25,20,0.35));
    }

    .overlay-card {
      position: absolute;
      z-index: 2;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.76);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(60, 44, 32, 0.1);
    }

    .overlay-top {
      top: 22px;
      left: 22px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      max-width: 250px;
    }

    .overlay-top small,
    .overlay-bottom small {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 7px;
    }

    .overlay-top strong,
    .overlay-bottom strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .overlay-bottom {
      right: 22px;
      bottom: 22px;
      width: min(270px, calc(100% - 44px));
      border-radius: 26px;
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .overlay-bottom ul {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 12px 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .overlay-bottom li {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(45,40,36,0.12);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .overlay-bottom li:last-child {
      border-bottom: 0;
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 44px 0;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: end;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .section-copy {
      max-width: 720px;
    }

    .section-copy span {
      display: inline-block;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .section-copy h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4vw, 4rem);
      line-height: 0.96;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .section-copy p {
      margin: 12px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.9;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .products-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .product-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.07);
      border-radius: 26px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .product-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 26px 46px rgba(67, 50, 38, 0.1);
    }

    .product-image {
      aspect-ratio: 1 / 1.08;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #f5efe8;
    }

    .product-image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform 0.35s ease;
    }

    .product-card:hover .product-image img {
      transform: scale(1.04);
    }

    .product-body {
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .product-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: start;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .product-body h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .price {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .product-body p {
      margin: 10px 0 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .tags {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .tag {
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(245, 239, 232, 0.95);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.06);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.92fr 1.08fr;
      gap: 22px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .about-photo,
    .about-card {
      border-radius: 34px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.07);
    }

    .about-photo {
      min-height: 560px;
      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1483695028939-5bb13f8648b0?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80') center/cover;
    }

    .about-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      padding: 32px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .about-card h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 3.2vw, 3rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      line-height: 0.98;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .about-card p {
      margin: 16px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.95;
    }

    .about-list {
      margin-top: 22px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .about-item {
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(246,241,234,0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.05);
    }

    .about-item strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }

    .about-item span {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-size: 0.93rem;
    }

    .values-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .value-card {
      padding: 26px;
      border-radius: 26px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.07);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .value-index {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: rgba(246,241,234,0.95);
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.06);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .value-card h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .value-card p {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.85;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .stats {
      margin-top: 22px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .stat {
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.07);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .stat strong {
      display: block;
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3rem);
      line-height: 0.95;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .stat span {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .testimonials {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .testimonial {
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 26px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.07);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .quote-mark {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      line-height: 0.8;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .testimonial p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.9;
      font-size: 0.96rem;
    }

    .testimonial strong {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .cta {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 38px;
      padding: 34px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5efe8, #fdfaf7);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.07);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .cta::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 240px;
      height: 240px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(185,170,151,0.12);
      top: -100px;
      right: -40px;
    }

    .cta-grid {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .cta h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      line-height: 0.95;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .cta p {
      margin: 12px 0 0;
      max-width: 760px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.9;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 42px 0 28px;
    }

    .footer-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 24px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,40,36,0.08);
    }

    .footer-grid p {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.85;
      margin: 14px 0 0;
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .footer-links h4 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 0.96rem;
    }

    .footer-links a,
    .footer-links span {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.93rem;
    }

    .copyright {
      margin-top: 24px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.86rem;
    }

    .whatsapp {
      position: fixed;
      right: 18px;
      bottom: 18px;
      z-index: 120;
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: #2f2a26;
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(47,42,38,0.18);
      border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
    }

    @media (max-width: 1120px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .about-grid,
      .cta-grid,
      .footer-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .products-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .values-grid,
      .testimonials,
      .stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .hero-card { min-height: 560px; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .nav-links,
      .desktop-only { display: none; }
      .menu-btn { display: inline-grid; place-items: center; }
      .hero { padding-top: 38px; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .container { width: min(calc(100% - 20px), var(--container)); }
      .products-grid,
      .values-grid,
      .testimonials,
      .stats,
      .footer-links { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-actions .btn,
      .cta .btn { width: 100%; }
      .hero-card {
        min-height: 500px;
        border-radius: 30px;
      }
      .overlay-top {
        top: 14px;
        left: 14px;
        right: 14px;
        max-width: none;
      }
      .overlay-bottom {
        left: 14px;
        right: 14px;
        bottom: 14px;
        width: auto;
      }
      .about-card,
      .cta,
      .testimonial,
      .value-card,
      .product-body { padding: 20px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="topbar">Pastelería artesanal · encargos personalizados · estética delicada</div>

  <header>
    <div class="container nav">
      <a href="#inicio" class="brand">
        <div class="brand-mark">✦</div>
        <div class="brand-copy">
          <strong>Atelier Sucré</strong>
          <span>Maison de pâtisserie</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="#coleccion">Colección</a>
        <a href="#nosotros">Nosotros</a>
        <a href="#detalle">Detalles</a>
        <a href="#opiniones">Opiniones</a>
        <a href="#contacto">Contacto</a>
      </nav>

      <div class="btn-row desktop-only">
        <a href="#coleccion" class="btn btn-secondary">Ver catálogo</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/5491112345678?text=Hola%20quiero%20hacer%20un%20pedido" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">Hacer pedido</a>
      </div>

      <button class="menu-btn" id="menuBtn" aria-label="Abrir menú">☰</button>
    </div>

    <div class="container mobile-panel" id="mobilePanel">
      <div class="mobile-links">
        <a href="#coleccion">Colección</a>
        <a href="#nosotros">Nosotros</a>
        <a href="#detalle">Detalles</a>
        <a href="#opiniones">Opiniones</a>
        <a href="#contacto">Contacto</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/5491112345678?text=Hola%20quiero%20hacer%20un%20pedido" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">Pedir por WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero" id="inicio">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Minimal · limpio · artesanal</div>
          <h1>Pastelería delicada con una estética serena y elegante.</h1>
          <p>
            Diseñamos cada producto con una lógica visual simple, tonos suaves y terminaciones cuidadas.
            Una identidad pensada para transmitir limpieza, detalle y una experiencia premium desde la primera mirada.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="https://wa.me/5491112345678?text=Hola%20quiero%20consultar%20por%20sus%20productos" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">Consultar por WhatsApp</a>
            <a href="#coleccion" class="btn btn-secondary">Explorar colección</a>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-notes">
            <div class="note-pill">Tortas personalizadas</div>
            <div class="note-pill">Box dulces</div>
            <div class="note-pill">Mesas para eventos</div>
          </div>
        </div>

